long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Whiteboard is a UI enhancement suite for The University of Texas at Dallas's online learning platform, eLearning. This extension provides a modern interface with useful features such as grades overview, weekly calendar, notifications, and much more. It also provides RateMyProfessor and UTDGrades information as additional columns on CourseBook.
